: cap read

-- Capability to crawl (AHMAD-BOT has this)
: cap crawl

-- Capability to propose fixes (EDUALC has this)
: cap propose_fix

-- Capability to seal (only BOB has this)
: cap seal

-- Capability to deploy (only SOVEREIGN has this)
: cap deploy

